{"tid":421353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我想尋狗呀 請幫幫我","createTime":"2017-10-02T07:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T07:48:31.000Z","uid":59678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a79a24b3368b5a3ede192cded721946eca5ce65","tid":421353,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/150928_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F150928_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c3a57b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿迷真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前揸住粒黑氣石咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/150933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F150933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4332f8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高普一定好有野心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家有野心到排係隊無野心既後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左上面果兩隻猁狗之外<br />\n我仲唔見左隻搶口鍾意咬人既猁狗<br />\n而家叫adidos<br />\n如果有清見到請幫我手捉返佢出黎<br />\n怕佢地深潛得耐缺氧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57df9db8dbafab435d4724a50ab2781b1ecc10eb","tid":421353,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a327674c523e4bc2edc02bc8f5e0278f875560ea","tid":421353,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"74698f65136db10715c568fafe857a4664bcc86f","tid":421353,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"幫手捉返佢地出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我怕佢地缺氧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ac999a8b745fa1d935d8d02671517df47e154f","tid":421353,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"我係一個好小氣既人，真係得罪我我會記著你幾年，即使今季鞭唔到你屍，唔緊要，將來幾季我鞭到你潛幾個月水，連自己個狗竇都唔敢入都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec91ed344bd727e42ca6d69c34ab4f5020862723","tid":421353,"uid":123243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 猁太多狗 難尋"},{"pid":"b280a9e0e51af26f36ea4d0a0e06b031662dd6c1","tid":421353,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"早排爆閘咬人果幾隻猁有無清可以幫手捉返佢地出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac91c2f7f7760138a4c114ba2b46404dea71c5e","tid":421353,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c51941ee934c067189c03a048ef01b5406d892","tid":421353,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/154738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F154738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=39b6bf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/154744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F154744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d33cff9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/154749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F154749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=00efbd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果三隻猁既示意圖<br />\n有清見到既就幫幫手捉返佢地出黎<br />\n我發現都係細狗鍾意咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}